  "titles": "Veteran Breacher Squad",
  "lore": "Rarer among most Legions than their Tactical and Assault counterparts, Veteran Breachers typically operated in a heavy assault capacity, serving offensively as linebreakers and defensively as an elite reserve. These capabilities saw them most frequently deployed in so-called ‘Zone Mortalis’ environments, their wargear affording them the resilience to endure such hellish warzones while their skill at arms – earned through decades at the forefront of the Great Crusade – saw them cut swathes through even the hardiest foes.",
